Author: CryptoDime
Title: [ITO] CryptoDime - Future's Virtual Present
Body: CRYPTODIME - FUTURE'S VIRTUAL PRESENT  28-March-2018: Public Token Sale has been cancelled as the hard cap was successfully reached. A huge thank you to everyone who participated in the token sale.   Home | About Us | CDM Token | Contest | Contact  Diversified Crypto Fund! CryptoDime provides an opportunity for investors looking for the simplest way to get into the decentralised economy.  CryptoDime was founded with an aim to implement management technologies with an immaculate track record in classical finance combined with rapidly growing crypto assets, and realize their fantastic potential. For investors, CryptoDime is a chance to enter the investment business with minimal funds and make money on the technologies that are used by all modern hedge funds.  Presale was limited to our existing investors only and was successfully ended on March 10th, 2018  PUBLIC SALE STARTS TODAY  1 ETH = 150,000  600,000 CDM  (All ICO subscribers are eligible to receive dividends)  If you have any questions or feedback, please do not hesitate to contact me by replying to this topic. Alternatively, you can also contact our support team from here. Our team of experts is ready to answer any question you may have.  Join Us  Facebook | Twitter | Telegram  Regards, Nick Sheldon
